Hey in my themes hubl code, when i put the header module inside the header block it doesnt show up. Does anybody have an idea why?
It works this way:
```&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;div class="body-wrapper {{ builtin_body_classes }}"&gt;
       {% block header %} {% endblock header %}
       {% module "header"
       path="@projects/basecom/app/components/modules/Header",
       no_wrapper=True %}
       &lt;div class="content"&gt;
          {% block body %} {% endblock body %}
          {% block footer %}
             {% module "footer"
                path="@projects/basecom/app/components/modules/Footer",
                no_wrapper=True %}
          {% endblock footer %}
       &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    {{ standard_footer_includes }}
&lt;/body&gt;```
